name: Admiral Ackbar (V)
Lore: 'Mon Calamari leader of Rebel fleet. Master military strategist. Early prisoner of Grand Moff Tarkin. Convinced his people to join the Alliance.',
Text: 'Adds 3 to power of anything he pilots. It''s a Trap! is destiny +2. Adds one battle destiny while piloting a Mon Calamari Star Cruiser. Once per game, may deploy a capital starship to a system (even as a ''react'') from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.',
